steps.name: Given The user is on the "stg" site
When The user clicks on the "try-volt" button
Then The user should be redirected to the "try-volt" page
When The user clicks on the "partners" button
Then The user should be redirected to the "partners" page
When The user clicks on the "no-compromises" button
Then The user should be redirected to the "no-compromises" page
When The user clicks on the "real-time-data-processing" button
Then The user should be redirected to the "real-time-data-processing" page
When The user clicks on the "capabilities_1" button
Then The user should be redirected to the "capabilities" page
When The user clicks on the "cloud-native" button
Then The user should be redirected to the "cloud-native" page
When The user clicks on the "high-availability" button
Then The user should be redirected to the "high-availability" page
When The user clicks on the "geo-replication" button
Then The user should be redirected to the "geo-replication" page
When The user clicks on the "capabilities_2" button
Then The user should be redirected to the "capabilities" page
When The user clicks on the "iot-at-the-edge" button
Then The user should be redirected to the "iot-at-the-edge" page
When The user clicks on the "streaming-data-platforms" button
Then The user should be redirected to the "streaming-data-platforms" page
When The user clicks on the "intersection-of-edge-iot" button
Then The user should be redirected to the "intersection-of-edge-iot" page
When The user clicks on the "capabilities_3" button
Then The user should be redirected to the "capabilities_2" page
Then Check for the console error on the page
